- ❌ Add unnecessary frameworks or libraries
- ❌ Create complex build processes
- ❌ Over-engineer simple features
- ❌ Add features not explicitly requested
- ❌ Change existing design without permission
- ❌ Create multiple CSS/JS files unless necessary

